Step 1) 
open "main-collection-product-grid" and add button for quick view. 

<button class="quick-view-btn absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-black text-white text-sm px-4 py-2 rounded opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" 
        data-handle="{{ product.handle }}"
        type="button">Quick View 
</button>

Step 2) 
create new file in snippets folder. "quick-view-model" and add code. 
then, call this file in theme.liquid file before </body> tag.

//quick view 
  {% render 'quick-view-model' %}

Step 3) 
add Javascript in theme.js file 

Step 4) 
create new file in section folder. "product-quick-view.liquid"

Step 5) 
create new file in template folder. "product.quick-view.liquid"


